data.description: Welcome to 521 Linden St in Reading! This townhome is brimming with desirable features. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a convenient laundry basement, this residence is designed for comfort and functionality. The main level welcomes you with a charming living room, dining area, kitchen, and easy access to the backyard. The second floor houses four bedrooms and a full bathroom. Don't miss the opportunity to schedule your showing today and explore the possibilities of making this your new home!
